the stretford wives is a british drama film made by the bbc . it was first broadcast on bbc one in august 2002 and has not been released on dvd . the film revolves around the lives of three sisters – played by fay ripley , claire rushbrook , and lindsey coulson – who live in stretford , greater manchester , england . written by shameless writer danny brocklehurst and directed by peter webber , it won critical acclaim from the times and the independent , although reviews in some local papers were not so favourable . the programme was watched by 5.7 million viewers .